Expansion of the Gebr. Heinemann headquarters In 2014, construction work began on the new expansion of the Gebr. Heinemann headquarters in the Magdeburg harbor area. As a complement to the existing buildings, the new building harmoniously completes the ensemble as a third striking structure. The material of the existing brick and the height development of the neighboring buildings are incorporated. Other historical elements have been reinterpreted. The new building was built in accordance with the requirements of the gold standard “Sustainable Building in HafenCity”
